# What are we doing here?

Weekly discussion to follow:

1) Assigned **readings**

2) Lectures held on the preceding Tuesday and Thursday

The immediate purpose of this class is for us all to dive into and come to understand
the writings of J. R. R. Tolkien better than we do now.

To that end, **everyone must read everything assigned every week.**

